==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cicuta
<hw>Ci*cu"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., the poison
hemlock.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>a genus of poisonous
umbelliferous plants, of which the water hemlock or cowbane is best
known.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The name <xex>cicuta</xex> is sometimes erroneously
applied to <xex>Conium maculatum</xex>, or <xex>officinal
hemlock</xex>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cicutoxin</ent>⟦br⟧
